---
<!-- Sección: Testimonios de Pacientes -->
<section class="testimonials-section" id="testimonios">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px;">
      <span class="section-subtitle">Testimonios</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Experiencias de pacientes recuperados</h2>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;">La tranquilidad de nuestros pacientes tras una cirugía exitosa es nuestro mejor respaldo.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials-carousel-wrapper">
      <button id="carouselPrev" class="carousel-control prev" aria-label="Testimonio anterior" disabled>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/></svg>
      </button>
      
      <div class="testimonials-track-container" id="carouselTrackContainer">
        <div class="testimonials-track" id="carouselTrack">
          <!-- Testimonio 1 -->
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="testimonial-rating">
              <!-- 5 Stars SVG -->
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="testimonial-quote">
              "Me operé de la vesícula por laparoscopía con el doctor. Desde la primera consulta en el Hospital San Juan de Dios me transmitió mucha calma. El dolor después de la cirugía fue mínimo y a los cinco días ya estaba caminando con normalidad. Muy agradecida por su profesionalismo y trato humano."
            </blockquote>
            <cite class="testimonial-author">
              <strong>María S.</strong>
              <span>Paciente de Colecistectomía Laparoscópica</span>
            </cite>
          </div>

          <!-- Testimonio 2 -->
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="testimonial-rating">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="testimonial-quote">
              "Tenía una hernia inguinal que me causaba muchas molestias al trabajar. El Dr. Vintimilla me explicó detalladamente las opciones y optamos por la técnica laparoscópica con malla. Todo salió excelente. Su experiencia de tantos años da mucha seguridad al paciente."
            </blockquote>
            <cite class="testimonial-author">
              <strong>Carlos R.</strong>
              <span>Paciente de Hernioplastia Laparoscópica</span>
            </cite>
          </div>

          <!-- Testimonio 3 -->
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="testimonial-rating">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="star-icon"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="testimonial-quote">
              "Acudí al consultorio del doctor para una segunda opinión sobre una eventración abdominal. Su diagnóstico fue sumamente honesto y claro, explicándome los riesgos reales. Me operó y la reconstrucción muscular fue perfecta. Su calidad humana es excepcional."
            </blockquote>
            <cite class="testimonial-author">
              <strong>Ana M.</strong>
              <span>Paciente de Pared Abdominal Compleja</span>
            </cite>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <button id="carouselNext" class="carousel-control next" aria-label="Siguiente testimonio">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="carousel-indicators" id="carouselIndicators">
      <button class="carousel-indicator active" data-slide="0" aria-label="Ir al testimonio 1"></button>
      <button class="carousel-indicator" data-slide="1" aria-label="Ir al testimonio 2"></button>
      <button class="carousel-indicator" data-slide="2" aria-label="Ir al testimonio 3"></button>
    </div>

    <!-- Google Reviews CTA -->
    <div class="google-reviews-cta" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 48px;">
      <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/9aP694PZswCjWq688" class="btn btn-secondary-outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M12.24 10.285V14.4h6.887c-.648 2.41-2.519 4.114-5.136 4.114-3.513 0-6.386-2.87-6.386-6.385s2.87-6.386 6.386-6.386c1.61 0 3.078.61 4.22 1.615l3.226-3.226C18.9 1.77 15.776.96 12.24.96c-6.1 0-11.04 4.94-11.04 11.04s4.94 11.04 11.04 11.04c6.387 0 11.458-4.5 11.458-11.04 0-.745-.078-1.3-.22-1.715H12.24z"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Ver todas las opiniones en Google</span>
      </a>
    </div>

<script>
  const track = document.getElementById('carouselTrack');
  const container = document.getElementById('carouselTrackContainer');
  const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.testimonial-card');
  const prevBtn = document.getElementById('carouselPrev');
  const nextBtn = document.getElementById('carouselNext');
  const indicators = document.querySelectorAll('.carousel-indicator');
  
  let currentIndex = 0;
  const totalSlides = cards.length;
  
  function updateCarousel(index) {
    if (index < 0) index = 0;
    if (index >= totalSlides) index = totalSlides - 1;
    currentIndex = index;
    
    // Apply transform translation only on wider screens where snap scroll isn't active
    if (window.innerWidth >= 768) {
      const offset = -currentIndex * 100;
      if (track) {
        track.style.transform = `translateX(${offset}%)`;
      }
    } else {
      // On mobile, scroll the container
      if (container) {
        const slideWidth = container.clientWidth;
        container.scrollTo({
          left: currentIndex * slideWidth,
          behavior: 'smooth'
        });
      }
    }
    
    // Update active class on indicators
    indicators.forEach((indicator, idx) => {
      indicator.classList.toggle('active', idx === currentIndex);
    });
    
    // Update button states
    if (prevBtn) prevBtn.disabled = currentIndex === 0;
    if (nextBtn) nextBtn.disabled = currentIndex === totalSlides - 1;
  }
  
  if (prevBtn && nextBtn) {
    prevBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      updateCarousel(currentIndex - 1);
    });
    
    nextBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      updateCarousel(currentIndex + 1);
    });
  }
  
  indicators.forEach(indicator => {
    indicator.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
      const targetSlide = parseInt(e.currentTarget.getAttribute('data-slide') || '0');
      updateCarousel(targetSlide);
    });
  });
  
  // Support swipe/scroll snap on mobile
  if (container) {
    let isScrolling;
    container.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
      window.clearTimeout(isScrolling);
      isScrolling = setTimeout(() => {
        if (window.innerWidth < 768) {
          const width = container.clientWidth;
          const scrollLeft = container.scrollLeft;
          const newIndex = Math.round(scrollLeft / width);
          if (newIndex !== currentIndex && newIndex >= 0 && newIndex < totalSlides) {
            currentIndex = newIndex;
            indicators.forEach((indicator, idx) => {
              indicator.classList.toggle('active', idx === currentIndex);
            });
            if (prevBtn) prevBtn.disabled = currentIndex === 0;
            if (nextBtn) nextBtn.disabled = currentIndex === totalSlides - 1;
          }
        }
      }, 100);
    });
  }
  
  // Set initial state
  updateCarousel(0);
  
  // Handle resize to adjust offsets
  window.addEventListener('resize', () => {
    if (window.innerWidth >= 768) {
      if (track) track.style.transform = `translateX(${-currentIndex * 100}%)`;
    } else {
      if (track) track.style.transform = 'none';
      if (container) container.scrollLeft = currentIndex * container.clientWidth;
    }
  });
</script>
  </div>
</section>
